### OpenAPI JSON
GET {{host}}/openapi/v1.json
Accept: application/json

### Realtime: Vehicles
# Podmieñ nazwê pliku jeœli inna (np. VehiclePositions_T.pb)
GET {{host}}/api/rt/vehicles?file=VehiclePositions.pb
Accept: application/json

### Realtime: Trip Updates
GET {{host}}/api/rt/trip-updates?file=TripUpdates.pb
Accept: application/json

### Realtime: Alerts
GET {{host}}/api/rt/alerts?file=ServiceAlerts_T.pb
Accept: application/json

### Static: Stops (z paczki GTFS zip)
GET {{host}}/api/static/stops?zip=GTFS_KRK_T.zip
Accept: application/json

### Static: Stops (wszystkie)
GET {{host}}/api/static/stops/all
Accept: application/json

### Static: Routes
GET {{host}}/api/static/routes?zip=GTFS_KRK_T.zip
Accept: application/json

### Static: Trips
GET {{host}}/api/static/trips?zip=GTFS_KRK_T.zip
Accept: application/json

### Enriched vehicles (bez TripUpdates)
GET {{host}}/v1/rt/vehicles/enriched?file=VehiclePositions.pb&zip=GTFS_KRK_T.zip
Accept: application/json

### Enriched vehicles (z TripUpdates -> lepszy next/eta/delay)
GET {{host}}/v1/rt/vehicles/enriched?file=VehiclePositions.pb&zip=GTFS_KRK_T.zip&tripUpdates=TripUpdates.pb
Accept: application/json

### On-route (multi ZIP, shapes-based) — bez heading
GET {{host}}/v1/map/routes/on-route?lat=50.065&lon=19.945&zips=all&radiusMeters=60
Accept: application/json

### On-route (z heading 90° = na wschód)
GET {{host}}/v1/map/routes/on-route?lat=50.065&lon=19.945&zips=all&radiusMeters=60&headingDeg=90
Accept: application/json

